管部門的生產許可。此外，這一生產線是全球首個且最大的新冠滅活疫苗生產線。加上武漢生物研究所的生產線產能，兩生產線可實現合計產能2.4億劑。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，8月20日、8月21日，大陸國藥集團中國生物分別與秘魯、摩洛哥以及阿根廷簽訂有關新冠滅活疫苗Ⅲ期臨床試驗的合作協議，這也意味著中國生物新冠滅活疫苗Ⅲ期臨床試驗全面提速。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:20:53.000Z","msg":"好快就會有2萬個政府職位空缺。"},{"pid":"413c948ffaab5092a6e6a98ad41955baf5813d34","tid":2171870,"uid":168555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T11:31:16.000Z","msg":"Biohazard 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4834d3b2371d7c5ea4c2643b06ec98acd19d2664","tid":2171870,"uid":198181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c985333df9e9c6494807a8f52962c465f602096c","tid":2171870,"uid":25560,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86566be9c9984263b5f77660299b0a68932454cb","tid":2171870,"uid":254547,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3db72726bb851d66a1b340eb4520c0805218fb5d","tid":2171870,"uid":133743,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:00:04.000Z","msg":"香港會唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"搵班香港公務員試 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"搵最高級香港公務員打左先, 之後由上而下層級咁接種?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"黑警畜牲啦，牠們日日要對住香港人，染支那毒病，畜牲自己全家中招唔撚怕，最怕害到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b3acd6cce362efedaaae0e87e783b7aa7c3fd8","tid":2171870,"uid":170848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:33:58.000Z","